OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781529076
OL,3,CHuman remains identified as man
OL,4,Cmissing since 2020
OL,6,FRemains of a man who went missing in
OL,7,FMay 2020 identified after being found
OL,8,Fsix years later.
OL,10,FThe remains belonged to Michael
OL,11,FDennington who was reported missing in
OL,12,FMay 2020 having last been seen at
OL,13,FKings Mill Hospital in Sutton-in-
OL,14,FAshfield.
OL,16,FThe remains were discovered around
OL,17,F2.45pm on Saturday 23 May in a wooded
OL,18,Farea next to the A617 Rainworth Bypass.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
